    and produces idiomatic R code. This is the gold standard for
    Translation translation quality.
    @End Reasoning

    Let source be proc string_from_literal from "x <- 42"

    Note: R → Tokens
    Let lexer be proc create_lexer from RLexer with source
    Let tokens be proc tokenize from RLexer with lexer
    Let token_count be proc get_token_count from RLexer with lexer

    Note: Tokens → AST
